00:06:47.461 --> 00:07:06.350
Incoming livestream: Where you can start to really pair these different levels of context together, to minimize noise. I think anyone that's done anomaly detection knows that it can be very noisy, especially if kind of deployed quickly. So, combining these three streams together, and then using them to kind of reduce noise across


