Incoming livestream: those kinds of anomalies. So, we started looking at how frequently were Agentic sessions accessing data? What types of access were they doing? Are… are the agents just selecting data? Are they updating it? Are they deleting it? Can we build filters or features around that?


82
00:07:54.721 --> 00:08:04.690
Incoming livestream: And so by keeping those feature sets simple, and the hypothesis simple, we started being able to investigate where does our coverage work versus where does it not work.


83
00:08:04.801 --> 00:08:12.221
Incoming livestream: We started to find out, what are the legitimate edge cases, what are the issues with what we're measuring, is it effective or is it not?


