00:15:51.321 --> 00:15:55.681
Incoming livestream: Ready when the deviation does occur, and then you can act on it immediately.


121
00:15:56.331 --> 00:16:04.631
Incoming livestream: Lesson number 3. Practitioners, ourselves included, often fall into the trap of building the perfect feature.


